sources.src/sass/main.sass:
@import reset.scss

// font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif  
// font-family: 'Fira Sans', sans-serif  
//  fonttitle. 

$branded: #332208
$white: #FEFEFE
$dark: #1B1818
$accent: #C5AC2D

$fonttitle: 'Fira Sans', sans-serif

a
    text-decoration: none

%top_btn
    background-color: $accent
    color: $white
    font-size: 16px
    line-height: 19px
    text-align: center
    text-transform: uppercase
    display: inline-block
    padding: 15px 18px
    border: 1px solid transparent
%top_hover
    color: $accent
    background-color: $white
    border: 1px solid $accent

.header
    background-color: $branded

.container
    max-width: 1200px
    margin: 0 auto
    padding: 0 10px

.header_inner
    display: flex
    justify-content: space-between
    align-items: center
    height: 100px

body
    font-size: 16px
    line-height: 19px
    font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif
    // font-family: 'Fira Sans', sans-serif

.menu_list
    display: flex

.menu_item
    margin-right: 30px
    &:last-child
        margin: 0

.menu_list-link
    text-transform: uppercase
    font-size: 18px
    line-height: 21px
    color: $white
    padding-bottom: 5px
    transition: .5s
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent
    font-weight: normal
    &:hover
        border-bottom: 1px solid $white

.phone
    font-size: 18px
    line-height: 21px
    color: $white
    font-weight: normal

.top
    padding-bottom: 100px

.top_info
    display: flex
    padding: 50px 0 30px

.top_content
    text-align: center
    padding-top: 90px
    width: 50%

.top_title
    font-size: 48px
    line-height: 58px
    color: $dark
    font-family: $fonttitle
    font-weight: 500
    margin: 0 auto 20px
    max-width: 455px

.top_text
    font-size: 24px
    line-height: 28px
    color: $dark
    margin: 0 auto 60px
    max-width: 470px

.application_btn
    transition: .5s
    @extend %top_btn
    &:hover
        @extend %top_hover

.swiper-container
    width: 100%
    height: 420px

.swiper-pagination
    display: flex
    flex-direction: column
    justify-content: center
    align-items: center

.swiper-container-vertical
    .swiper-pagination-bullets
        .swiper-pagination-bullet
            width: 8px
            height: 8px
            background: $dark
            opacity: 1
            &-active
                width: 16px
                height: 16px

.swiper-container-vertical
    .swiper-pagination-bullets
        right: 1px !important
        top: 53% !important

.top_slider
    max-width: 600px
    width: 100%
    display: flex
    flex-direction: column
    text-align: center

.top_slider-text
    padding-left: 100px
.slider_text-main
    font-family: $fonttitle
    font-weight: normal
    margin-top: 10px
    text-align: center
    span
        padding-left: 15px

.top_bottom
    display: flex
    align-items: flex-end
.top_items
    width: 50%
    display: flex
    justify-content: space-around

.top_item
    display: flex
    flex-direction: column
    align-items: center
    justify-content: space-around
    text-align: center
    border: 1px solid #332208
    box-shadow: (0px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25))
    width: 150px
    height: 150px
    padding: 0 10px
    cursor: pointer
    transition: .5s ease all
    &:hover
        transform: scale(1.25)

.top_links
    margin-left: 165px

.top_link
    color: $dark
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1B1818
    margin-left: 20px
    &:first-child
        margin: 0

.rent
    padding: 100px 0

.rent_inner
    display: flex
    justify-content: space-between

.rent_content
    width: 300px

.rent_title
    font-family: $fonttitle
    font-size: 24px
    font-weight: 500
    line-height: 29px
    color: $dark
    margin-bottom: 30px

.rent_main-text
    margin-bottom: 20px
    &:nth-last-child(2)
        margin-bottom: 40px

.rent_items
    border: 1px solid #332208
    box-shadow: (0px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25))
    width: 250px
    min-height: 350px
    padding: 0 30px 20px
    text-align: center

.rent_item-num
    font-family: $fonttitle
    opacity: 0.05
    font-size: 96px
    line-height: 115px

.rent_item-title
    font-family: $fonttitle
    color: $dark
    font-weight: 500
    font-size: 18px
    line-height: 22px
    margin-bottom: 30px

.benefits
    padding: 100px 0

.benefits_title
    font-family: $fonttitle
    font-weight: 500
    font-size: 24px
    line-height: 29px
    margin-bottom: 35px

.benefits_inner
    display: flex
    align-items: center

.benefits_items
    display: flex

.benefits_list
    width: 300px

.benefits_list-item
    margin-bottom: 27px
    padding-right: 26px
    position: relative
    text-align: right
    &::after
        content: ""
        width: 16px
        height: 16px
        background: $dark
        border-radius: 10px
        position: absolute
        right: 0
        top: 2px
    &:nth-child(1)
        margin-right: 10px
    &:nth-child(7)
        margin-right: 10px
    &:nth-child(2)
        margin-right: 55px
    &:nth-child(6)
        margin-right: 55px
    &:nth-child(3)
        margin-right: 105px
    &:nth-child(5)
        margin-right: 105px
    &:nth-child(4)
        margin-right: 150px

.benefits_content
    text-align: right

.benefits_main-text
    margin-bottom: 30px

.video_popup
    background-color: $accent
    color: $white
    text-transform: uppercase
    padding: 6px 34px 6px 64px
    text-align: center
    display: inline-block
    position: relative
    max-width: 200px
    &::before
        content: ""
        width: 25px
        height: 25px
        position: absolute
        background-image: url(../images/videopop.svg)
        bottom: 12px
        left: 34px

.reviews
    background: $branded
    padding: 100px 0
    color: $white

.reviews_top-slider
    width: 100%
    height: 100%
    overflow: hidden
    position: relative

.top_slider-wrapper
    display: flex
    justify-content: space-between
    width: 100%
    height: 100%
    

.slide_item
    display: flex
    justify-content: space-between
    flex-shrink: 0
    width: 100%
    height: 100%
    margin-bottom: 45px

.reviews_title
    font-size: 24px
    line-height: 29px
    color: $white
    font-family: $fonttitle
    margin-bottom: 70px

.reviews_item
    display: flex
    flex-direction: column
    justify-content: space-between
    padding: 45px 30px
    width: 270px
    min-height: 300px
    border: 1px solid #C5AC2D
    text-align: center

.reviews_item-title
    font-family: $fonttitle
    font-size: 24px
    line-height: 29px
    color: $white
    text-align: center
    margin-bottom: 50px

.reviews_item-text
    text-align: center

.top_slider-pag
    display: flex
    flex-direction: row

.top_slider-pag
    .swiper-pagination-bullet
        background: #C5AC2D
        opacity: 1
        &-active
            width: 16px
            height: 16px

.feedback
    padding: 100px 0

.feedback_wraper
    display: flex
    align-items: center

.feedback_imgages
    width: 50%

.feedback_title
    font-family: $fonttitle
    font-size: 24px
    line-height: 29px
    font-weight: 500
    margin-bottom: 5px

.feedback_text
    margin-bottom: 30px
    color: $dark

.feedback_form
    width: 415px
    margin: 0 auto
    display: flex
    flex-direction: column
    position: relative

.feedback_input
    display: block
    padding: 20px 0
    width: 100%
    border: none
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, .1)
    &::placeholder
        line-height: 19px
        font-size: 16px
        color: $dark
        font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif

.feedback_btn
    text-transform: uppercase
    color: $white
    border: none
    display: inline-block
    background-color: $accent
    margin-top: 50px
    font-size: 16px
    line-height: 19px
    max-width: 200px
    height: 50px
    transition: .5s
    &:hover
        @extend %top_hover

.footer
    background-color: $branded
    padding-top: 80px

.footer_top
    display: flex
    justify-content: space-between
    align-items: center
    margin-bottom: 35px

.footer_bottom
    display: flex
    justify-content: center
    padding-bottom: 10px

.socail_item-links
    margin-left: 30px

.social_item-images
    &:hover
        transform: scale(1.3)

.menu_btn
    display: none

@media (max-width: 1000px)
@media (max-width: 860px)
    .header_menu
        order: 1
    .menu_list
        display: block
        position: absolute
        top: 100px
        left: 0
        right: 0
        background-color: $branded
        padding: 20px 0
        transform: translateY(-500px)
        transition: all .5s
    .menu_list.menu_list--active
        transform: translateY(0px)
    .menu_list-link
        padding: 20px 0
        display: block
        text-align: center
    .menu_btn
        display: block
        width: 30px
        height: 25px
        border: none
        cursor: pointer 
        border-top: 2px solid #fefefe
        border-bottom: 2px solid #fefefe
        background-color: transparent
        position: relative
        &::before
            content: ""
            position: absolute
            width: 30px
            height: 2px
            background-color: #fefefe
            left: 0
            top: 9px
